{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/TestClock","doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/UnimplementedClock"],"title":"Implementations","generated":true}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"ImmediateClock","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"s:6Clocks14ImmediateClockC","modules":[{"name":"Clocks"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ImmediateClock"}],"title":"ImmediateClock","symbolKind":"class","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/Tyler-Keith-Thompson\/Afluent\/blob\/main\/.build\/checkouts\/swift-clocks\/Sources\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock.swift#L111","fileName":"ImmediateClock.swift"},"platforms":[{"name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"16.0"},{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"13.0","name":"macOS"},{"introducedAt":"16.0","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"name":"tvOS","beta":false},{"beta":false,"name":"watchOS","unavailable":false,"introducedAt":"9.0","deprecated":false}]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/clocks\/immediateclock"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ImmediateClock"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Duration","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Duration"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s16DurationProtocolP","text":"DurationProtocol"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Duration"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SH","text":"Hashable"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This clock is useful for squashing all of time down to a single instant, forcing any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"sleep"},{"type":"text","text":"s"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to execute immediately."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For example, suppose you have a feature that needs to wait 5 seconds before performing some","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"action, like showing a welcome message:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct Feature: View {","  @State var message: String?","","  var body: some View {","    VStack {","      if let message = self.message {","        Text(self.message)","          .font(.largeTitle.bold())","          .foregroundColor(.mint)","      }","    }","    .task {","      do {","        try await Task.sleep(for: .seconds(5))","        self.message = \"Welcome!\"","      } catch {}","    }","  }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This is currently using a real life clock by calling out to ","type":"text"},{"code":"Task.sleep(for:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", which means"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"every change you make to the styling and behavior of this feature you must wait for 5 real life"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"seconds to pass before you see the affect. This will severely hurt your ability to quickly"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"iterate on the feature in an Xcode preview.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The fix is to have your view hold onto a clock so that it can be controlled from the outside:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct Feature: View {","  @State var message: String?","  let clock: any Clock<Duration>","","  var body: some View {","    VStack {","      if let message = self.message {","        Text(self.message)","          .font(.largeTitle.bold())","          .foregroundColor(.mint)","      }","    }","    .task {","      do {","        try await self.clock.sleep(for: .seconds(5))","        self.message = \"Welcome!\"","      } catch {}","    }","  }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This code is nearly the same as before except that it now holds onto an explicit clock. This","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"allows you to use a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ContinuousClock"},{"type":"text","text":" when running on a device or simulator, and use an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock"},{"type":"text","text":" when running in an Xcode preview:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","code":["struct Feature_Previews: PreviewProvider {","  static var previews: some View {","    Feature(clock: .immediate)","  }","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Now the welcome message will be displayed immediately with every change made to the view. No"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"need to wait for 5 real world seconds to pass, making it easier to iterate on the feature."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can also propagate a clock to a SwiftUI view via the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"continuousClock"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"suspendingClock"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"environment values that ship with the library:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct Feature: View {","  @State var message: String?","  @Environment(\\.continuousClock) var clock","","  var body: some View {","    VStack {","      if let message = self.message {","        Text(self.message)","      }","    }","    .task {","      do {","        try await self.clock.sleep(for: .seconds(5))","        self.message = \"Welcome!\"","      } catch {}","    }","  }","}","","struct Feature_Previews: PreviewProvider {","  static var previews: some View {","    Feature()","      .environment(\\.continuousClock, .immediate)","  }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A clock that does not suspend when sleeping."}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Clocks\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/Clocks\/12_Concurrency5ClockP"]}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Creating-immediate-clocks","identifiers":["doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock\/init(now:)","doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock\/init()"],"title":"Creating immediate clocks"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock\/Instant"],"anchor":"Structures","title":"Structures"},{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock\/minimumResolution","doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock\/now"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"title":"Instance Methods","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock\/sleep(until:tolerance:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock\/Clock-Implementations","doc:\/\/Clocks\/documentation\/Clocks\/ImmediateClock\/Clock-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"references":{"doc://Clocks/documentation/Clocks/ImmediateCl